  "detailed_description": "Conqueror Of Time is a traditional dungeon crawl rogue game with a time travel theme. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610030/extras/7a679184e503395e07f747f557fe0f0a.avif?t=1716199670\" width=640 height=434 /></span><br><br><br>Choose a character from different time periods and fight your way through dungeons using various items from different times and spaces. <br>Battle against enemies such as pirates, dinosaurs, aliens, robots, and Vikings. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610030/extras/825d62ce52e05c48111648589072e07e.avif?t=1716199670\" width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610030/extras/2b5217538b4ca9e2a834cdb0c434b01a.avif?t=1716199670\" width=640 height=232 /></span><br><br>Level up your character and gain new Time Abilities.<br>Use time travel abilities to fight alongside your past or future self.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610030/extras/4e116e4743446ef804201032bb595d04.avif?t=1716199670\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>Features:<br>Unique characters, enemies, weapons, and items<br>Random maps each time<br>Travel through time and fight along side your self<br>Unlock new characters<br>Turn-based strategy<br>Fight in the Past, Present, and Future",
  "about_the_game": "Conqueror Of Time is a traditional dungeon crawl rogue game with a time travel theme. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610030/extras/7a679184e503395e07f747f557fe0f0a.avif?t=1716199670\" width=640 height=434 /></span><br><br><br>Choose a character from different time periods and fight your way through dungeons using various items from different times and spaces. <br>Battle against enemies such as pirates, dinosaurs, aliens, robots, and Vikings. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610030/extras/825d62ce52e05c48111648589072e07e.avif?t=1716199670\" width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610030/extras/2b5217538b4ca9e2a834cdb0c434b01a.avif?t=1716199670\" width=640 height=232 /></span><br><br>Level up your character and gain new Time Abilities.<br>Use time travel abilities to fight alongside your past or future self.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2610030/extras/4e116e4743446ef804201032bb595d04.avif?t=1716199670\" width=640 height=360 /></span><br><br>Features:<br>Unique characters, enemies, weapons, and items<br>Random maps each time<br>Travel through time and fight along side your self<br>Unlock new characters<br>Turn-based strategy<br>Fight in the Past, Present, and Future",
